<br>
At your level tank.  Tank, tank, tank - keep your defense up...you will need it when you get in groups and slow on a regular basis in your high levels.<br>
<br>
When you get to the root and dot phase (I didn't start doing this until middle 40's)... pull mob (I used the malo line for pulling)... root mob where you want it - sic pet.  After pet goes for it, slow mob, dot mob (root will break usually).  When root breaks, re-root mob or reverse kite (keep dots on and run around in circles while puppy beats on mob). I was solo'ing yellow and red named in Skyfire with this method at 45.  <br>
<br>
Don't expect puppy to be a tank, he sucks as a tank (until 61 - or so everyone tells me).<br>
<br>
But at your younger levels - use the getting beat on as an excuse to raise that defense.<br>
<br>
