<br>
One of them is fast casting but short duration. It *seems* to have a better chance of lasting for the full duration.<br>
<br>
The other casts more slowly but has the potential to last longer. It also *seems* to have a greater likelyhood of breaking early.<br>
<br>
Later on, (after 60 I think) we get one of each line that has a much greater chance of landing and holding. (It has a negative resist modifier.) A lvl65 shaman can root-park a beastie and more-or-less forget about it until the group is ready to attend to it. (I'm not 65, but I've seem some good ones in action.)<br>
<br>
At 61, I'm finding that my highest-level root spell is getting fairly reliable. It is possible that I'm just now learning what to expect of it, hehe, but it isn't surprising me nearly as much as it used to. Even now I really only use root for crowd-control. I think I used the root-n-rot technique once, maybe twice. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.showPrevMessage?topicID=144.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.showNextMessage?topicID=144.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=144.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.threadControl?topicID=144.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=144.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=144.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing